            "rendered": "#cloud-config\n---\nhostname: Rocky-Linux\nfqdn: Rocky-Linux.midominio.org\nmanage_etc_hosts: true\n\nusers:\n  - name: nicolas.fuentes2024\n    sudo: ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD:ALL\n    groups: wheel\n    home: /home/nicolas.fuentes2024\n    shell: /bin/bash\n    lock_passwd: false\n    ssh-authorized-keys:\n      - ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzaC1lZDI1NTE5AAAAIB3kM6zQ6tKfRYCJx2XelUTbEQ066RqzUEkpMNmcANxA nicolas.fuentes2024\n\n\nssh_pwauth: true\ndisable_root: false\n\nchpasswd:\n  expire: false\n  list:\n    - nicolas.fuentes2024:linux\n\npackages:\n  - qemu-guest-agent\n  - python3\n  - glibc-langpack-es\n\nruncmd:\n  - localectl set-locale LANG=es_CL.UTF-8\n  - localectl set-keymap latam\n  - localectl set-x11-keymap latam pc105\n  - echo \"Cloud-Init termino exitosamente la configuracion\" \u003e /root/bootcmd.log\n\nfinal_message: \"The system is finally up, after $UPTIME seconds\"",
